The only human example that has a hair color that is simply impossible as opposed to improbable would be {{champion:37}} 

We have every reason to believe in the world that {{champion:254}} {{champion:245}}  and {{champion:222}} dyed their hair with their rebellious personalities. Sona very well could have, but it doesn't seem like her to do that. 

The white haired ladies {{champion:22}} {{champion:164}} {{champion:131}} {{champion:40}} {{champion:92}} fall into the realm of unlikely, but not impossible.
